{"id":155393,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/05/红外卫星照片发现17座失落的埃及金字塔/","date":"2011-05-26T00:00:45Z","modified":"2011-05-26T00:00:45Z","title":"红外卫星照片发现17座失落的埃及金字塔","content":"<p>红外卫星照片揭示出17座被埋起来的金字塔，超过1000座古墓和3000个古代定居点。初步挖掘证实了卫星的发现，已有两座金字塔出土。 伯明翰阿拉巴马大学空间考古学家Sarah Parcak的团队，分析了卫星从700公里轨道上拍摄的高分辨率红外照片，照片能识别出直径小于一米的目标。研究人员相信能发现更多古代建筑物。<img border=\"0\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://solidot.org.feedsportal.com/c/33236/f/556826/s/15358a17/mf.gif\" width=\"1\" /></p>\n<div>\n<table border=\"0\">\n<tr>\n<td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://res.feedsportal.com/viral/sendemail2.html?title=%E7%BA%A2%E5%A4%96%E5%8D%AB%E6%98%9F%E7%85%A7%E7%89%87%E5%8F%91%E7%8E%B017%E5%BA%A7%E5%A4%B1%E8%90%BD%E7%9A%84%E5%9F%83%E5%8F%8A%E9%87%91%E5%AD%97%E5%A1%94&#038;link=http%3A%2F%2Fscience.solidot.org%2Farticle.pl%3Fsid%3D11%2F05%2F25%2F1036218%26amp%3Bfrom%3Drss\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/images/emailthis2.gif\" /></a></td>\n<td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://res.feedsportal.com/viral/bookmark.cfm?title=%E7%BA%A2%E5%A4%96%E5%8D%AB%E6%98%9F%E7%85%A7%E7%89%87%E5%8F%91%E7%8E%B017%E5%BA%A7%E5%A4%B1%E8%90%BD%E7%9A%84%E5%9F%83%E5%8F%8A%E9%87%91%E5%AD%97%E5%A1%94&#038;link=http%3A%2F%2Fscience.solidot.org%2Farticle.pl%3Fsid%3D11%2F05%2F25%2F1036218%26amp%3Bfrom%3Drss\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/images/bookmark.gif\" /></a></td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n</div>\n<p><a href=\"http://da.feedsportal.com/r/101094052649/u/49/f/556826/c/33236/s/15358a17/a2.htm\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://da.feedsportal.com/r/101094052649/u/49/f/556826/c/33236/s/15358a17/a2.img\" /></a></p>\n<div>\n<a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/solidot?a=La-lanZ4xto:p_zKdojYPWI:yIl2AUoC8zA\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/solidot?d=yIl2AUoC8zA\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/solidot?a=La-lanZ4xto:p_zKdojYPWI:7Q72WNTAKBA\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/solidot?d=7Q72WNTAKBA\" /></a>\n</div>